lead_paragraph: Ben Bentil and Kris Dunn provided a frontcourt-backcourt one-two punch that Georgetown couldn't contain as No. 10 Providence held off several second-half charges for a 73-69 victory on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Dunn, Bentil Help No. 10 Providence Fend Off Georgetown
